NoSQl Categories
================

Key/Value (Ex: Firebase)
Document (Ex: MongoDb, CouchDb)
Column (Ex: Casandra)
Graph (Ex: )

Firebase Essentials
===================

1. It is Key/Value Database that looks like a Document Db 
2. Hosted, you don't need to install It
3. Url-oriented 
4. Real-time



